      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">stanza</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·006.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">南山.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>葛屨五兩，冠緌雙止。魯道有蕩，齊子庸止。既曰庸止，曷又從止！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The five kinds of dolichos shoes are made in pairs,
And the string-ends of a cap are made to match;
The way to Loo is easy and plain,
And the daughter of Ts'e travelled it.
Since she travelled it,
Why do you still follow her?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-qifeng-006__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
