      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·006.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">南山.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>蓺麻如之何？衡從其畝。取妻如之何？必告父母，既曰告止，曷又鞠止！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How do we proceed in planting hemp?
The acres must be dressed lengthwise and crosswise.
How do we proceed in taking a wife ?
Announcement must first be made to our parents.
Since such announcement was made,
Why do you still indulge her desires?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-qifeng-006__004__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
