      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·006.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">南山.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>析薪如之何？匪斧不克。取妻如之何？匪媒不得，既曰得止，曷又極止！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How do we proceed in splitting firewood ?
Without an axe it cannot be done.
How do we proceed in taking a wife?
Without a go-between it cannot be done.
Since this was done,
Why do you still allow her to go to this extreme ?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
